Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:23.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tia, sister, can I have your~ advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you once~ more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:32.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Have you ever felt crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the guilt that you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:41.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hold inside despite the love~ of your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the strength that~ they~ lent?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A feel~ing so lingering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Leaving you spent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:17.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I can still recall the way~ that~ it felt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:20.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,On my own in isolation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:26.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Kept away from hurting all that~ I loved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:33.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the jealousy that I let~ my~self have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:37.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And though I'm trying to heal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:45.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's hard to let go~ of the past that I made so real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:51.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I've missed you~ so~ dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:55.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it's been far too long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:00.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can you ever forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For what I did~ wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Luna sister I am so sorry for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the ways I~ ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:20.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How unhappy you felt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:24.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the burdens you bore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:29.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Those years ago still fresh in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:34.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Through the passing of time~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I won't let our past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Mask the joy of your return
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:05.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A thousand winters finally come to a close
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:08.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As a spring approaches to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:14.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Erase the frozen wasteland left in the wake~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And after all this time we can finally
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:22.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fly in the cool night sky~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And frolic running through the fields
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:30.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We can spend time together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:34.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like we should have all those years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:39.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So please don't be sad Lu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm just glad you're back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:55.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm just grateful to have you home